name: "Hooty-Cho" Tissue Pouch
description:
This little darling is the most adorable packet of tissues, you must have in the car, school bag, diaper bag, sewing bag, golf bag or just in the handbag as even though most would use this as a tissue pouch- it is the perfect size to discreetly hold your feminine products too! The tissue packet cover is made from 100% cotton and will protect your tissues from getting grimy. 

~ Ensuring no embarrassment when the need arises to offer a friend a tissue ~

Great quality cotton prints to bring a smile to your face.  Fully machine washable, though may need a press (or not! LOL) 

Includes a packet of Kleenex tissues that measure 21cm x 21cm.
